Hi, Here are some VIP services which are usually hard to get at Kumbh Mela:

*VIP Darshan & Special Access Passes*
- These allow direct access to bathing ghats and temples, bypassing long queues.
- Typically reserved for political figures, celebrities, and top bureaucrats.

*Akharas & Private Camps Entry*
- Some prestigious Akharas have private camps that are invitation-only.
- Gaining entry requires strong religious or political connections.

*Premium Tents & Luxury Camps*
- The best accommodations, like luxury tents and premium cottages, are booked months in advance.
- These include 24/7 security, attached bathrooms, and gourmet food.

*Helicopter Rides & Aerial Darshan*
- Some services offer helicopter rides for an aerial view of the Kumbh.
- Bookings are expensive and fill up quickly.

*Private Boat Access for Snan (Holy Dip)*
- VIPs sometimes get private boats to avoid crowds during peak bathing days.
- These require special permissions.
